com.mcc.ul
Class MemInfo

java.lang.Object
  com.mcc.ul.MemInfo

public class MemInfo
extends java.lang.Object

This class provides methods to retrieve information about the memory region on a DAQ device. To create an instance of this class, call the getMemInfo() method of the DaqDeviceInfo class.
